{
  "stem": "753.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't hear from her again, nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no mail, nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some rumors-- I can't tell you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I never discussed this with my other sister because I never thought I will have to kind of record it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I think there was some postcard from her from Sarajevo, which was a big surprise to my parents, and a horrible disappointment, knowing that she is in the middle of the worst part of war.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But she was incognito there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she left with this boyfriend and a girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I will backtrack a little bit now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This girlfriend survived the war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she told us the following.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They arrived to Sarajevo.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were thrown in jail right away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were beaten up in jail terribly, all three of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But they didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They just didn't talk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They, they didn't have what to say.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the milkman that was bringing them milk into the jail was a partisan.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This was already the beginning of underground and the resistance, 1941.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And Tito was forming his 1st Proletarian Brigade beginning of 1941.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And this brigade consisted of the hard-core communists and, of course, people that were fighting anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There were some Jews there, not few-- many-- and people that were anti-fascist that decided they're going to fight whatever the way they can.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And this underground-- somebody from the underground-- because her boyfriend was already connected with the underground-- who was bringing milk into the jail on a cart saved those three people, got them out.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And in this cart covered with rags, they get-- got out of the jail.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then she joined the 1st Proletarian Brigade with this girlfriend and with him.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
